data.description: Can you really have it all?! you can and today is your lucky day! In the highly sought Springfield School district, this 4-bedroom house offers a great deck overlooking a huge fenced in backyard.  Don't forget the 3-car garage and numerous walk-in closets!!  Newer kitchen, and 2 full baths make this a can't miss opportunity.  Also did I mention first floor laundry?!  See the rest that this beauty has to offer for yourself! Schedule your private showing today!
